<h3 id="aggregateerror-errors" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#aggregateerror-errors" aria-hidden="true">#</a> AggregateError(errors)</h3>
<p>Returns an <code v-pre>Error</code> that is also an <a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Guide/Iterators_and_Generators#Iterables" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><code v-pre>Iterable</code><ExternalLinkIcon/></a> for the individual errors.</p>
<h4 id="errors" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#errors" aria-hidden="true">#</a> errors</h4>
<p>Type: <code v-pre>Array&lt;Error|Object|string&gt;</code></p>
<p>If a string, a new <code v-pre>Error</code> is created with the string as the error message.<br>
If a non-Error object, a new <code v-pre>Error</code> is created with all properties from the object copied over.</p>
